# Colors and Styling

**NEVER hardcode colors.** Use CSS variables and utility classes from `src/app/globals.css`.

## Text colors

- Colored backgrounds: `text-hero-heading`, `text-hero-body`
- Footer: `text-footer`, `text-footer-muted`
- Default: `text-heading`, `text-body`, `text-muted`, `text-nav`
- On primary bg: `text-on-primary`

## Backgrounds

`bg-page`, `bg-surface`, `bg-surface-secondary`, `bg-surface-tertiary`, `bg-primary`, `bg-primary-hover`, `bg-primary-dark`, `bg-placeholder`

## Buttons

`btn-hero-primary`, `btn-hero-secondary`, `btn-cta`, `btn-nav`, `btn-nav-mobile`, `btn-primary`, `btn-secondary`

## Borders

`border-primary`, `border-primary-hover`, etc.

## Dark mode

Themes live in `globals.css` (`:root` and `.dark`). Use `ThemeProvider` from `@/app/components/common` — never hardcode light/dark colors in components.

## Exception

Hex colors belong **only** in `src/app/globals.css`.

```tsx
// ❌ BAD
className="text-white bg-gray-200"
style={{ color: "#00AEEF" }}

// ✅ GOOD
className="text-on-primary bg-surface"
```
